{"tid":2248735,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"是日笑話: 中國通過新專利法  稱將嚴懲侵權行為  以回應美國批評","createTime":"2020-10-18T23:05:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T00:45:29.000Z","uid":204533,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"be06fd97e696f68d2096f17327fa2b01fb7bd918","tid":2248735,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國通過修改的專利法，將法定賠償額提高，增加侵害智慧財產權的成本，相關做法回應了中美第一階段貿易協議的要求。新法將從2021年6月實施。中國修法期間正逢中美貿易戰，中國對智慧財產權保護不力受到批評。<br />\n<br />\n據主要是今天報道說，中國修法提高侵權賠償，呼應中美貿易協議。該報道引述中國央視及新京報消息，中國13屆全國人大常委會第22次會議17日昨天通過修改專利法的決定，其中對故意侵權行為規定1到5倍的懲罰性賠償，將法定賠償額上限提高至人民幣500萬元）、下限提高至3萬元。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201018-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%95%E5%9A%B4%E7%BD%B0%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A-%E5%91%BC%E6%87%89%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E7%88%AD%E7%AB%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20201018-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259A%25B4%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%25AC%258A-%25E5%2591%25BC%25E6%2587%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%25AB%25AF&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a67XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=34a8546c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20201018-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%95%E5%9A%B4%E7%BD%B0%E4%BE%B5%E6%AC%8A-%E5%91%BC%E6%87%89%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E7%88%AD%E7%AB%AF</a>"},{"pid":"4bb622946713642872a366f0b3159ee4302e2438","tid":2248735,"uid":78971,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T23:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去到呢個地步先嚟做啲咁多嘅嘢<br />\n十足十小學生開頭串柒柒，<br />\n到被老師罰留堂見家長喇，<br />\n就趴低扮晒乖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2d7f218e11d48c0734cd0d110d5c0417b1ba14"